Farm Fresh Barbecue Party!

Come enjoy fresh local food and live music, and meet Farmers To You!

Each week Farmers To You delivers custom orders of local craft foods to neighborhoods throughout Cambridge and the Boston metro area. Join us on Thursday, May 23rd to learn about our partnership of families and farmers while enjoying a farm fresh spring barbeque and live music at our Harvard/Porter Sq. pickup site.

Bring Your Friends!
